file_content.text: Can't wait to get all this sand out of my boots. Can we leave this party?
Master Kiwiiks... she's alive. She's asking to talk to you.
I can barely feel Master Kiwiiks anymore. We need to hurry.
I can sense Master Kiwiiks in pain. We need to find her.
Not sure which climate is worse... Taris or Tatooine. Maybe a tie?
